description.8: Daimon requests a conversation with none other than Doctor Strange! Hellstorm's occultist origin is revealed. And it's a doozy.
description.12: Guest-starring Darkhawk! The Pacific Overlords have returned. But what is Dr. Demonicus's truly plotting?
description.16: Can Daredevil fight the demons of his past, the collective fears of the city, and a new villain all at the same time?!
description.18: Under Mentallo's hypnosis, Hulk teams up with Juggernaut. The strongmen go head-to-head against Earth's Mightiest- but who's really bringing the might?
description.22: We know the Vulture from modern day Spider-Man, but what does he look like in 2099? Miguel comes face-to-face with a dangerous new foe, who may still have ties to the past.
description.23: The Dark Valkyrie spins poisonous lies in Thor's ear, leading to heated conflict with Beta Ray Bill!
description.27: The FF are summoned to the moon by the Watcher! What evil is so dire that it could force Uatu to break his vow of non-interference? Who else...but DOOM?
description.29: Who is Epsilon Red? Could he be the key to Wolverine unlocking more of his memories?
description.32: Captain Mar-Vel continues his adventures on earth by taking on the identity of Dr. Walter Lawson. This puts him on the path of meeting security chief Carol Danvers, and a Kree Sentry with commands to kill!
description.38: Daimon Hellstrom, Son of Satan, tries on a new role for size-head cleric at the Black School for mystic arts! But an imposter Son of "Satan" nearly robs him of his spot…
description.41: The return of Styx and Stone! Spider-Man crosses paths with Cardiac while investigating a shadowy filmmaker. Plus, trouble on the home front when MJ's job is threatened!
description.42: Ikaris of the Eternals arrives to bring Sersei back home, but it ends with Sersei becoming soul-bonded with Black Knight. But then why is Black Knight hitting on Crystal?
description.43: When A.I.M. are found drilling the Savage Lands for vibranium, Captain America teams up with Black Panther and Kazar to stop them!
description.49: The battle with Decimator and Tokamak rages on! But can the newly-formed Secret Defenders stand up to them when they're joined by a mysterious new foe: DREADLOX!?
description.53: Deadzone continues the beatdown on Moon Knight!
description.57: Hawkeye's taken up a new mantle as the super-sized powerhouse Goliath. Unfortunately, the villain also named Goliath has taken some umbrage with this.
description.62: Daredevil is known as a man without fear, but the new villain, known as Shock, might change that!
description.64: The Hulk has been defeated! Juggernaut's imprisoned him in Red Skull's hideout. And it only gets worse! Mentallo launches a psychic attack on Hulk, hypnotizing the not-so-jolly-giant to attack the Avengers!
description.68: Spider-Man falls under (literal) fire with the Public Eye, a terrorizing group of thugs that claim to fight in the public's defense. But who exactly does the Public Eye work for? And who is upholding the law in the crooked streets of New York?
description.69: Thor struggles with his return to Asgard post-banishment.
description.73: The Fantastic Four face one of their toughest battles yet - against the Secret Defenders! Can the FF stand up to Wolverine, Spider-Man, Ghost Rider, and the Hulk?
description.75: Can the X-Men track down Maverick in time to find and stop a disoriented Wolverine from killing?
description.80: Deadzone has Moon Knight at his mercy.  Will Marc Spector escape with his life?
description.85: The climactic showdown between Spider-Man and Venom! Spidey calls on a ghost from Eddie Brock's past to assist his takedown of Venom and the retrieval of his parents. But will Venom fall for the bait? J. Jonah Jameson calls in the big guns of Silver Sable and her Wild Pack!
description.86: The Gatherers dispatch an alternate dimension Vision to kill the Swordsman. Can the Avengers stop this would-be assassin. Plus, the return of a fan-favorite Avenger!
description.87: It's a hostile takeover as M.O.D.A.M. captures Superia! Will Captain America risk it all to save one super villain from another?
description.96: Doctor Strange! Wolverine! Spider-Woman! Nomad! Darkhawk! Banding together, they form...the Secret Defenders! And together they'll face a trial by fire, as they combat the deadly threat of Decimator and Tokamak!
description.97: Love cures all! Moe Walter's cry of love for the Weezi he fell in love with persuades Weezi to switch back bodies with She-Hulk.
description.98: Captain Zero and Brainstorm connect the dots from their past, and Spider-Man is trapped in the fallout!

0.text: Morbius and Martine Bancroft do unholy battle! After which, Morbius is transformed into a real, undead vampire!

1.text: Demons…on a plane! Professor Hastings' daughter puts up a good fight, but will she be able to escape this living nightmare?

2.text: Saul and Gideon have Boomer, Warpath and Siryn dangling off a cliff! Tina meets a tragic fate while contemplating a jewel heist with Vanessa.

4.text: In this thrilling What If? tale, we explore what would come to pass if Silver Surfer wielded the Infinity Gauntlet instead of Thanos!

7.text: MAXIMUM CARNAGE PART 1 Carnage has returned and he's ready to bring his brand of murder and mayhem to New York.  But when Carnage adopts like-minded allies, it becomes Maximum Carnage. Can Spider-Man, Venom and others stop him?

9.text: Cable has come from the future with a warning for the X-Men but is he too late?

10.text: The Russian government recruits Illyana to stop the Soul Skinner!

12.text: Guest-starring Darkhawk! The Pacific Overlords have returned. But what is Dr. Demonicus's truly plotting?

13.text: Graymalkin is set to explode, and there's only one person besides Cable who can deactivate the ticking time bomb! Meanwhile, Deadpool is on the hunt for Vanessa and Tina…who hit the town as "twins"!

14.text: Eternity calls on Adam Warlock and he must answer. The best, and worst, past lives of Warlock are merged into one cosmic entity. Warlock receives a prophecy and magical orb from Eternity. Who are the five beings that will define Warlock’s future?

17.text: Cap and Meggan fight the Warpies in an attempt to save their fellow heroes- and are brought to Cloud Nine!

19.text: Iron Man and War Machine, side-by-side for the first time! When Stark is beset by Battledroids, it's Rhodes to the rescue! But don't think these two friends are getting along now, 'cause Rhodey's still furious over Stark's lies! Will their friendship ever mend? (Originally published as IRON MAN (1993) #291)

29.text: Who is Epsilon Red? Could he be the key to Wolverine unlocking more of his memories?

31.text: The Silver Surfer battles Captain Atlas and Doctor Minerva!

36.text: Nightmare sets a trap designed for Strange by first taking control of Morbius! Now, the Doctor’s physical body belongs to Nightmare!

37.text: Castle and Ice Philips continue their fight against a fringe cell causing terroristic acts!

44.text: Heroes from around the world battle with demons!

45.text: When our heroes stop off on the water planet Aquaris to meet with new Rebel allies, they find that at least one of those allies may be an Imperial spy. Han and Leia both have plans to trap the traitor by using Luke's droids as bait, but their plans may go awry when Luke and Han wind up in the clutches of a deadly denizen of the deep!

46.text: Adam Warlock and his Infinity Watch have sworn to recover Shalla-Bal. But the crew’s not off to a great start! After opening a dimensional portal chock full of demons, Surfer and company find themselves in the thrall of cosmic battle. Which portal will lead to Shalla-Bal’s dimension? And even if her body is found, will her soul still be intact?

47.text: The new Galactic Guardians face off against the powerful Bubonicus!

48.text: Cage agrees to an exchange of services for information on his father and brother. Dr. Karl Malus unleashes Coldfire!

49.text: The battle with Decimator and Tokamak rages on! But can the newly-formed Secret Defenders stand up to them when they're joined by a mysterious new foe: DREADLOX!?

50.text: When She-Hulk receives news that John Byrne is dead, she must try and decide which writer and artist will take the reins on her series.

52.text: Romulus and Gideon of X-Force battle it out, but we all know it's not a party until Nick Fury gets involved!

54.text: The foe behind the Darkforce possession is at long last revealed!

55.text: Featuring Scarlet Witch! In the second half of their Maui duel, Doc Strange triumphs over Modred after much spellcasting and trickery.

56.text: The X-Men do battle with Omega Red and the Soul Skinner while in Russia!

57.text: Hawkeye's taken up a new mantle as the super-sized powerhouse Goliath. Unfortunately, the villain also named Goliath has taken some umbrage with this.

58.text: After a satellite launch accident, Cable's ship Graymalkin is unveiled in Earth's orbit! It's a race to space for X-Force and S.H.I.E.L.D.!

59.text: Gamora proves that she is ‘Iron Man strong’ while fighting UN troops on Monster Isle. Devastation is wrought; Gamora stands triumphant. Pip puts the moves on the Most Dangerous Woman in the Galaxy. Bad idea, Pip.

63.text: Smythe pushes Nightcrawler's powers to the max. Meanwhile, Rachel and the Phoenix Force come face-to-face with Death...

65.text: Tony Stark returns from the dead! Morgan Stark makes his move for control of Stark Enterprises! And no sooner is Tony back in command of his new suit of armor then he's attacked on all sides by weapon-wielding warriors! (Originally published as IRON MAN (1993) #290)

75.text: Can the X-Men track down Maverick in time to find and stop a disoriented Wolverine from killing?

77.text: The Silver Surfer and Jack of Hearts clash with Nebula and an army of space pirates!

79.text: Nick Fury and Solo take on Viper. The only thing she has are nuclear weapons on her side!

81.text: The Darkforce has taken over the New Warriors, and is now pitting the team against each other!

82.text: Doctor Strange and Modred the Mystic take their dark magic duel to a true destination...Maui!

83.text: Who are the underground dwelling mutants known as the Morlocks and what do they want with the X-Men?

84.text: Mys-Tech sends demons to attack Earth's heroes!

91.text: While taking a stroll, Rintrah encounters a dangerous cult whose source of power is an ancient, arcane evil!

92.text: The Punisher partners up with an old army buddy to take on a paramilitary terrorist cell.

93.text: Nothing will stop Cage in the pursuit of his brother and father…not even Hardcore! Luke’s closest relatives are being held hostage by this dangerous madman. Will Cage find the answers he needs before it’s too late?

94.text: The Resurrection begins! Although he lost part of himself when he became the Silver Surfer, Norrin Radd can never forget the woman he loved from his days on Zenn-La. With Shalla-Bal’s death never far from his thoughts, the Surfer is more haunted than ever. But when Pip the Troll delivers a message from Adam Warlock, Surfer’s hope sparks anew. Warlock claims Shalla-Bal is alive! But if so, where is she?

95.text: Yellowjacket joins the Guardians! The team also meets Krugarr, the Sorcerer Supreme of the 31st century!

96.text: Doctor Strange! Wolverine! Spider-Woman! Nomad! Darkhawk! Banding together, they form...the Secret Defenders! And together they'll face a trial by fire, as they combat the deadly threat of Decimator and Tokamak!

97.text: Love cures all! Moe Walter's cry of love for the Weezi he fell in love with persuades Weezi to switch back bodies with She-Hulk.

98.text: Captain Zero and Brainstorm connect the dots from their past, and Spider-Man is trapped in the fallout!

99.text: Colossus is reunited with his family in Russia!
